data.description: Welcome to your new home located in the Historical District of Lancaster. This impeccably designed brick front home with 3 bedroom, 2 bath is a sanctuary of style, convenience, and relaxation. The spacious living area has 12FT exposed beam ceiling flaring visual elegance with a wood-burning fireplace boasts a stylish room perfect for a cozy evening. Two large spilt bedrooms each room is a serene haven with bay windows providing ample space, can be considered double main bedrooms. Main Bedroom bathroom has oversized jetted tub and separate shower. Newly installed Berber carpet, fresh paint touch ups, and new doors. Double garage can be used as workshop.Extra large driveway for extra parking perfect to park your RV’s.  Peach tree in the front yard and the fenced in backyard is ready for you to enjoy. Seller is including the additional plot of land to the back of the property to convey with sale already fenced in. Swing by today to make this house your home. No HOA small quaint community.
